<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ms">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= editMode === 'create' ? 'Cipta Kumpulan Baru' : 'Edit Kumpulan' %> - Admin</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <div class="min-h-screen p-8">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-8">
            <div class="mb-6">
                <a href="/admin-mace/groups" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 text-sm mb-4 inline-block">&larr; Kembali ke Senarai Kumpulan</a>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900"><%= editMode === 'create' ? 'Cipta Kumpulan Baru' : 'Edit Kumpulan' %></h1>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Kumpulan menentukan modul mana yang boleh diakses oleh pelajar melalui enrollment key.</p>
            </div>

            <% if (editMode === 'edit' && group) { %>
                <form action="/admin-mace/groups/edit/<%= group._id %>" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Nama Kumpulan</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" value="<%= group.name %>" required placeholder="Cth: Intake Julai 2024" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Penerangan</label>
                        <textarea name="description" rows="3" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none"><%= group.description || '' %></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Guru Penanggungjawab</label>
                        <select name="teacherId" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none bg-white">
                            <option value="">-- Pilih Guru --</option>
                            <% (teachers || []).forEach(t => { %>
                                <option value="<%= t._id %>" <%= group.teacherId && group.teacherId._id.toString() === t._id.toString() ? 'selected' : '' %>><%= t.fullName %> (<%= t.email %>)</option>
                            <% }) %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Modul Diberikan</label>
                        <select name="moduleIds" multiple class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none bg-white h-40">
                            <% (modules || []).forEach(m => { %>
                                <option value="<%= m._id %>" <%= group.modules && group.modules.some(mod => mod._id.toString() === m._id.toString()) ? 'selected' : '' %>><%= m.title %></option>
                            <% }) %>
                        </select>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Tahan Ctrl/Cmd untuk pilih lebih dari satu modul</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Enrollment Key</label>
                        <input type="text" name="enrollmentKey" value="<%= group.enrollmentKey %>" readonly class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 font-mono">
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Kongsi key ini dengan pelajar untuk sertai kumpulan. Reset di halaman senarai jika perlu.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Maksimum Pelajar (0 = tiada had)</label>
                        <input type="number" name="maxStudents" value="<%= group.maxStudents || 0 %>" min="0" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none">
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="isActive" id="isActive" <%= group.isActive ? 'checked' : '' %> class="rounded border-gray-300 text-blue-600 focus:ring-blue-500">
                        <label for="isActive" class="text-sm text-gray-700">Kumpulan Aktif</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pt-4 flex gap-3">
                        <button type="submit" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition">Simpan Perubahan</button>
                        <a href="/admin-mace/groups" class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition">Batal</a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            <% } else { %>
                <form action="/admin-mace/groups/new" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Nama Kumpulan</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="Cth: Intake Julai 2024" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Penerangan</label>
                        <textarea name="description" rows="3" placeholder="Penerangan ringkas tentang kumpulan ini" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Guru Penanggungjawab</label>
                        <select name="teacherId" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none bg-white">
                            <option value="">-- Auto-assign kepada Admin (boleh edit kemudian) --</option>
                            <% (teachers || []).forEach(t => { %>
                                <option value="<%= t._id %>"><%= t.fullName %> (<%= t.email %>)</option>
                            <% }) %>
                        </select>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Jika tidak dipilih, kumpulan akan dipertanggungjawabkan kepada admin yang mencipta. Boleh ditukar kemudian.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Modul Diberikan</label>
                        <select name="moduleIds" multiple class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none bg-white h-40">
                            <% (modules || []).forEach(m => { %>
                                <option value="<%= m._id %>"><%= m.title %></option>
                            <% }) %>
                        </select>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Tahan Ctrl/Cmd untuk pilih lebih dari satu modul</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Enrollment Key (Optional - auto-generate jika kosong)</label>
                        <input type="text" name="enrollmentKey" placeholder="Biarkan kosong untuk auto-generate" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none font-mono">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Maksimum Pelajar (0 = tiada had)</label>
                        <input type="number" name="maxStudents" value="0" min="0" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none">
                    </div>
                    <div class="pt-4 flex gap-3">
                        <button type="submit" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition">Cipta Kumpulan</button>
                        <a href="/admin-mace/groups" class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition">Batal</a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
